{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Infinium: A Spaceboy's Tale is a classic, 2D platform adventure game with arcade elements. You follow a captivating story of a young boy named Leo, who set out on the journey of a lifetime. Accompany him, fulfil his dreams and fight hostile creatures while discovering diverse lands of the solar system.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore various environments</strong>  <br>Traverse across multiple planets and defeat unique enemies. <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/EnviroVariety2WithShadowSmallV2_NewestV2.gif?t=1739184607\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Master the art of platforming movement</strong><br>Enjoy a simple, yet satisfying character movement model, which over time is enhanced by new skills, such as dash, jetpack or double jump. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/MarsVarietyMovement3WithShadowSmallV3.gif?t=1739184607\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fly your spaceship</strong><br>Old-school and fun mini-game where you steer a spaceship.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/SpaceShipWithShadowSmallV3_Newest.gif?t=1739184607\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Complex tale of\u00a0Leo</strong> <br>A fascinating, linear story complemented by dialogues, music and cutscenes.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/extras/Cutscene3WithShadowSmall_Newest.gif?t=1739184607\" /></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075610/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739184607","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st